metadata.name: Dreamscape - Fade Away Between Roses
metadata.description:
Nude portrait captured with 35mm analog film.

Muse: Eve M.

(2653x4000px. Full frame JPG)

“Dreamscape” is a mystic series exploring the beauty of women, details and a magical natural place in Colombia.

“Show me how you smile with your wet lips.
She's morphine on my mind when I'm coming down.
I feel like I have lived this Déjà vu, send me a vision of you.
I wanna take you down, your lies make it hurt and you want the same thing. Better to fade between roses.”
